title: I Want To Pack  Her Up And Put Her Out
itunes:title: I Want To Pack  Her Up And Put Her Out
description:
Dear Steve and Shirley, I am writing you because I need advice. A friend of mine was going through a rough time recently and she and her 4 children ended up getting evicted from their apartment. Me, being the caring and big-hearted person that I am, I offered to let my friend and the children stay with me temporarily till she got herself together. She initially said she’d only need three months and assured me that she would be looking for a place to live daily.....................
